{"_path":"/shi-ling-cheng","_dir":"","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"釋靈澄","children":[{"title":"西來意頌","content":["因僧問我西來意，我話居山七八年。","草履只栽三箇耳，麻衣曾補兩番肩。","東庵每見西庵雪，下澗長流上澗泉。","半夜白雲消散後，一輪明月到床前。"],"tags":[]}],"_id":"content:shi-ling-cheng.json","_type":"json","_source":"content","_file":"shi-ling-cheng.json","_extension":"json"}